pr_body:
#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -

1. Adds `base_controller.rb` for shared error handling and `pagination`.
2. Adds following authentication API (using `jwt-token`) endpoints:
    - Authentication
        - `api/v1/auth/signup` for new users.
        - `api/v1/auth/login` for already existing users.
    - Users
        - `api/v1/users/` to list all users.
        - `api/v1/me` to get the details of logged in user.
        - `api/v1/users/:id` to `GET` and `PATCH` user details.

3. Adds custom matcher for `have_json_api_errors` and `json_schema_matcher`.
5. Use schemas to better test the API responses.
4. Adds `authentication_spec` and `users_spec`.

### The `docs` are available [here](https://nitish145.github.io/slate/)


Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

pr_body:
#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -

1. Adds the following projects endpoints:
    -  `api/v1/projects` to fetch all public or user accessible projects.
    -  `api/v1/users/:id/projects` to fetch user specific projects.
    -  `api/v1/projects/:id` to GET, UPDATE & DELETE project details.
    -  `api/v1/projects/featured` to fetch featured projects.
    -  `api/v1/projects/:id/toggle-star` to star/unstar a project.
    -  `api/v1/projects/:id/fork` to fork a project.

2. Add project/projects schema.

3. Add specs for each of the projects controller actions.

### The updated `docs` are available [here](https://nitish145.github.io/slate/)

Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -
1. Adds the following Groups endpoints
    - `/api/v1/groups` to fetch all groups.
    - `/api/v1/groups_mentored` to fetch the groups you mentor
    - `/api/v1/groups/` to POST a new group.
    - `/api/v1/groups/:id/` to GET, UPDATE, DELETE group details.

2. Adds the following Group Members endpoints
    - `/api/v1/groups/:group_id/group_members` to GET all the group members or POST new group member.
    - `/api/v1/group_members/:id/` to DELETE any group member.

3. Adds the following Assignments endpoints
    - `/api/v1/groups/:group_id/assignments` to GET all assignments for a group or POST new assignment
    - `/api/v1/assignments/:id` to GET assignment details, PATCH or DELETE assignment.
    - `/api/v1/assignments/:id/reopen` to reopen a closed assignment.
    - `/api/v1/assignments/:id/start` to start working on any assignment

4. Add Groups, Group Members, Assignments schema

5. Add specs for each of the possible test cases.

### The updated `docs` are available [here](https://nitish145.github.io/slate/)

Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -
1. Adds the following collaborators endpoints
    - `/api/v1/projects/:project_id/collaborators` to GET & POST collaborators.
    - `/api/v1/projects/:project_id/collaborators/:id` to DELETE a collaborator.

2. Add specs for each controller action and possible test cases.

### The updated `docs` are available [here](https://nitish145.github.io/slate/)

Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

1. Adds the following grading endpoints
    - `api/v1/assignments/:assignment_id/projects/:project_id/grades` to grade assignment.
    - `api/v1/grade/:id` to update & destroy grade.

2. Adds validation to `project_id` & `assignment_id` in grades.

3. Adds grades schema & specs

pr_body:
#### Describe the changes you have made in this PR -

1. Add threads endpoints.
    - close thread `/api/v1/threads/:id/close`
    - reopen thread `/api/v1/threads/:id/reopen`
    - subscribe thread `/api/v1/threads/:id/subscribe`
    - unsubscribe thread `/api/v1/threads/:id/unsubscribe`

2. Add comments endpoints
    - GET thread's comments `/api/v1/threads/:thread_id/comments`
    - POST new comment `/api/v1/threads/:thread_id/comments`
    - UPDATE comment `/api/v1/comments/:id`
    - Delete, Undelete, Upvote, Downvote, Unvote comment.

3. Format `routes.rb`.
4. Cleanup `base_controller.rb`.
5. Add extensive specs for threads & comments API. 


Note: Please check **Allow edits from maintainers.** if you would like us to assist in the PR.

pr_title: Set Up the basic folder structure, views, viewmodels and services
pr_body:
This PR adds the following changes:

- Adds basic project structure.
- Adds the dialog service, managers and models.
- Adds the navigation service to navigate without context.
- Adds local storage service using shared preferences.
- Adds base views and viewmodels.
- Wire up home, login and startup view/viewmodel.
